- Using Make: ---------------------------------------------------

 To install:

  $ make
  $ make install

  Edit /etc/slapt-getrc (see README for details)

 To uninstall:

  $ make uninstall

- Using pkgtools: -----------------------------------------------

 To install:

  $ make pkg
  $ installpkg ./pkg/slapt-get-${VERSION}-${ARCH}-${RELEASE}.tgz

 To uninstall:
  $ removepkg slapt-get-${VERSION}-${ARCH}-${RELEASE}
